<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{ doc.numero }} · Manifiesto de Carga</title>
<style>
  {{ fontStyle | raw }}
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; }
  :root { --ink: #1a2720; --ink-2: #48554e; --ink-3: #7b8882; --accent: #1d6b4f; --accent-2: #d1e7dc; --accent-soft: #f2f8f5; --line: #d9e0dc; --paper: #fdfdfb; }
  body { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.45; color: var(--ink); background: var(--paper); width: 1123px; min-height: 794px; padding: 30px 40px; }
  .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  p { margin: 0; }

  .top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; align-items: start; gap: 28px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .brand .mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .brand .logo { width: 42px; height: 42px; flex: none; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .brand .logo svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; }
  .brand .logo img { max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; object-fit: contain; }
  .brand .co-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
  .brand .co-tagline { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 1px; }
  .brand .meta { margin-top: 9px; font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-2); max-width: 560px; }
  .doc-id { text-align: right; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 16px; }
  .doc-id .tag { font-size: 8.5px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .doc-id .kind { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.05; margin-top: 3px; }
  .doc-id .num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 2px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .doc-id .meta2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto auto; gap: 2px 12px; font-size: 9px; margin-top: 9px; justify-content: end; }
  .doc-id .meta2 .k { color: var(--ink-3); white-space: nowrap; text-align: left; }
  .doc-id .meta2 .v { font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; text-align: right; }

  .sec-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 9px; }
  .sec-head .t { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }
  .sec-head .c { font-size: 9px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ink-3); font-weight: 600; }

  .items-wrap { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
  .items { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; }
  .items thead th { font-size: 8.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 600; text-align: left; padding: 10px; background: var(--accent-soft); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .items tbody td { padding: 9px 10px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); vertical-align: top; font-size: 9.5px; }
  .items .c-fecha { width: 70px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-serie { width: 96px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: var(--accent); }
  .items .c-taquito { width: 104px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-placa { width: 70px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-bul, .items .c-weight, .items .c-flete { text-align: right; }
  .items .c-bul { width: 52px; font-weight: 600; }
  .items .c-weight { width: 78px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .items .c-flete { width: 84px; font-weight: 600; }
  .items .c-pago { width: 100px; }
  .items .party { font-weight: 500; word-break: break-word; }
  .items .pago .pill { display: inline-block; font-size: 8px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.02em; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .pago .pill.cancelado { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
  .items .pago .pill.cobrar { background: var(--accent-2); color: var(--accent); }
  .items .pago .pill.pce { border: 1px solid var(--line); color: var(--ink-2); }
  .items tfoot td { padding: 9px 10px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 9.5px; }
  .items tfoot .lbl { text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .items tfoot .c-bul, .items tfoot .c-weight, .items tfoot .c-flete { text-align: right; color: #fff; }
  .items tfoot .c-flete { padding-left: 6px; }

  .foot { margin-top: 18px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .foot .note { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .foot .note strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .foot .note .badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; background: var(--accent-2); color: var(--accent); padding: 4px 11px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 8.5px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .foot .note .badge::before { content: ""; width: 5px; height: 5px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top">
  <div class="brand">
    <div class="mark">
      <div class="logo">{% if params.logo is not empty %}<img src="{{ params.logo }}" alt="logo"/>{% else %}<svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.4"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="14"/><path d="M9 23l5-9 6 4 6-7"/></svg>{% endif %}</div>
      <div>
        <div class="co-name">{{ doc.emisorRazonSocial }}</div>
        {% if doc.emisorNombreComercial is not empty and doc.emisorNombreComercial != doc.emisorRazonSocial %}<div class="co-tagline">{{ doc.emisorNombreComercial }}</div>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta">{% if doc.emisorDireccion is not empty %}{{ doc.emisorDireccion }} · {% endif %}{% if doc.emisorUbicacion is not empty %}{{ doc.emisorUbicacion }} · {% endif %}{% if doc.emisorRegistroMtc is not empty %}Reg. MTC {{ doc.emisorRegistroMtc }} · {% endif %}{% if doc.emisorEmail is not empty %}{{ doc.emisorEmail }} · {% endif %}{% if doc.emisorTelefono is not empty %}{{ doc.emisorTelefono }} · {% endif %}RUC {{ doc.emisorRuc }}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="doc-id">
    <div class="tag">Documento interno</div>
    <div class="kind">Manifiesto de Carga</div>
    <div class="num">{{ doc.numero }}</div>
    <div class="meta2">
      <span class="k">Fecha de salida</span><span class="v">{% if doc.fechaSalida is not null %}{{ doc.fechaSalida|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</span>
      {% if doc.serie is not empty %}<span class="k">Serie · N°</span><span class="v">{{ doc.serie }} · {{ doc.numero }}</span>{% endif %}
      <span class="k">Guías · bultos</span><span class="v">{{ doc.totalGuias }} · {{ doc.totalBultos }}</span>
      <span class="k">Peso · flete</span><span class="v">{{ doc.totalPeso|n_format }} kg · S/ {{ doc.totalFlete|n_format }}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sec-head"><span class="t">Carga consolidada — guías de remisión</span><span class="c">{{ doc.totalGuias }} guías</span></div>
<div class="items-wrap">
<table class="items">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th class="c-fecha">F. Emisión</th>
      <th class="c-serie">Serie · N°</th>
      <th class="c-taquito">N° Tracking</th>
      <th>Remitente</th>
      <th>Destino</th>
      <th class="c-placa">Placa</th>
      <th class="c-weight">Peso kg</th>
      <th class="c-bul">Bultos</th>
      <th class="c-flete">Flete S/</th>
      <th class="c-pago">Pago</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for l in doc.lineas %}
    <tr>
      <td class="c-fecha mono">{% if l.fechaEmision is not null %}{{ l.fechaEmision|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</td>
      <td class="c-serie mono">{{ l.guiaSerieNumero }}</td>
      <td class="c-taquito mono">{{ l.taquito }}</td>
      <td class="party">{{ l.remitente }}</td>
      <td class="party">{{ l.destinoDistrito }}</td>
      <td class="c-placa mono">{{ l.placa }}</td>
      <td class="c-weight mono">{{ l.peso|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-bul mono">{{ l.bultos }}</td>
      <td class="c-flete mono">{{ l.flete|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="pago">{% if l.condicionPago is not empty %}<span class="pill {{ l.pagoClase }}">{{ l.condicionPago }}</span>{% endif %}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl" colspan="6">Total · {{ doc.totalGuias }} guías consolidadas</td>
      <td class="c-weight mono">{{ doc.totalPeso|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-bul mono">{{ doc.totalBultos }}</td>
      <td class="c-flete mono">{{ doc.totalFlete|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-pago"></td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
</div>

<div class="foot">
  <div class="note">
    <span class="badge">Uso interno</span>
    <p>Documento de <strong>control de carga consolidada</strong> para el viaje. No constituye comprobante de pago ni guía de remisión electrónica; cada guía se sustenta de forma individual.</p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
